This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to:
- The Tolkien Estate
- Middle-earth Enterprises
- Amazon Studios
- Any official Tolkien properties or adaptations

EDUCATIONAL USE STATEMENT

This software is created for educational, research, and non-commercial purposes:
- To study and preserve Tolkien's linguistic creations
- To provide tools for language learning and academic research
- To support the scholarly community studying constructed languages
- To enable creative writing and artistic expression

LINGUISTIC CONTENT NOTICE

The Elvish languages (Quenya, Sindarin, etc.) were created by J.R.R. Tolkien.
This project contains:
- Scholarly reconstructions based on published materials
- Community-developed extensions and interpretations  
- Linguistic analysis and educational commentary
- No direct copying of copyrighted narrative content

FAIR USE JUSTIFICATION

Use of linguistic elements is believed to constitute fair use under copyright law:
- Transformative educational purpose
- Scholarly analysis and commentary
- Non-commercial academic application
- Minimal use necessary for linguistic study
- No market harm to original works

