- The Grey Company language developers
- The broader Tolkien linguistics community

CONTENT MODIFICATION POLICY

Users of this software may:
- Use the linguistic data for educational purposes
- Modify and extend the vocabulary for academic research
- Create derivative tools for language learning
- Contribute improvements and corrections

ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS

When using this software or its data:
- Credit the original linguistic sources as listed above
- Include this license notice in redistributions
- Acknowledge the educational and research nature of the content
- Respect the scholarly tradition of Tolkien linguistics

LIMITATION OF LIABILITY

The linguistic content is provided for educational purposes only. Accuracy of
translations, etymologies, and grammatical analyses cannot be guaranteed.
Users should verify information against primary sources for academic work.

COMMUNITY CONTRIBUTION

This project supports the open scholarly study of constructed languages.
Contributions, corrections, and improvements are welcomed under the same
educational and non-commercial principles.

